	<owl:Class rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/AggregationDescription">
		<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationContentEntity"/>
		<rdfs:subClassOf>
			<owl:Restriction>
				<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/describes"/>
				<owl:allValuesFrom rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000027"/>
			</owl:Restriction>
		</rdfs:subClassOf>
		<rdfs:isDefinedBy>https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/InformationSlot/</rdfs:isDefinedBy>
		<owl:equivalentClass>
			<owl:Class>
				<owl:intersectionOf rdf:parseType="Collection">
					<rdf:Description rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/DescriptiveInformationContentEntity">
					</rdf:Description>
					<owl:Restriction>
						<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/hasSlot"/>
						<owl:someValuesFrom rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/CountSlot"/>
					</owl:Restriction>
				</owl:intersectionOf>
			</owl:Class>
		</owl:equivalentClass>
	</owl:Class>
	
	<owl:Class rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/AssemblySpecification">
		<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/DesignSpecification"/>
		<rdfs:isDefinedBy>https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/InformationSlot/</rdfs:isDefinedBy>
	</owl:Class>
	
	<owl:Class rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/ComponentParthoodSlot">
		<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationSlot"/>
		<rdfs:subClassOf>
			<owl:Restriction>
				<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/hasFiller"/>
				<owl:allValuesFrom>
					<owl:Class>
						<owl:intersectionOf rdf:parseType="Collection">
							<rdf:Description rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationContentEntity">
							</rdf:Description>
							<owl:Restriction>
								<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/isAbout"/>
								<owl:allValuesFrom rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/MaterialComponent"/>
							</owl:Restriction>
						</owl:intersectionOf>
					</owl:Class>
				</owl:allValuesFrom>
			</owl:Restriction>
		</rdfs:subClassOf>
		<rdfs:subClassOf>
			<owl:Restriction>
				<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/isSlotOf"/>
				<owl:someValuesFrom>
					<owl:Class>
						<owl:intersectionOf rdf:parseType="Collection">
							<rdf:Description rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationContentEntity">
							</rdf:Description>
							<owl:Restriction>
								<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/isAbout"/>
								<owl:allValuesFrom>
									<owl:Class>
										<owl:intersectionOf rdf:parseType="Collection">
											<rdf:Description rdf:about="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000004">
											</rdf:Description>
											<owl:Class>
												<owl:complementOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000006"/>
											</owl:Class>
										</owl:intersectionOf>
									</owl:Class>
								</owl:allValuesFrom>
							</owl:Restriction>
						</owl:intersectionOf>
					</owl:Class>
				</owl:someValuesFrom>
			</owl:Restriction>
		</rdfs:subClassOf>
		<rdfs:label xml:lang="en">component parthood slot</rdfs:label>
		<rdfs:isDefinedBy>https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/InformationSlot/</rdfs:isDefinedBy>
		<skos:example>A system specification has a &apos;component parthood slot&apos; filled by a component specification, thereby prescribing that the specified system must &apos;has component part&apos; the specified component for conformance to the specification; an inspection report has a &apos;component parthood slot&apos; filled by a component description, thereby reporting that the inspected system &apos;has component part&apos; the described component</skos:example>
		<annotation:explanatoryNote>1) If slot of a prescriptive host, the slot specifies that conformance requires having the filled material component as a component part. If slot of a reporting host, the slot records that the host’s referent has the filled material component as a component part.
2) The LA2 axiom cant be formalized on the component parthood slot in OWL and it should be utilized instead on the ICEs that the slot &apos;is the slot of&apos;</annotation:explanatoryNote>
		<annotation:firstOrderLogicAxiom>LA2: ComponentParthoodSlot(x) → ∀z, y, c, m ( (slotOf(x,z) ∧ hasFiller(x,y) ∧ isAbout(z,c) ∧ isAbout(y,m)) → (hasComponentPartAtSomeTime(c,m) ∨ (prescribes(z,c) ∧ (conformsTo(c,z) → hasComponentPartAtSomeTime(c,m)))) )</annotation:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
		<annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition>information slot that is slot of an information content entity that is about an independent continuant, that can be filled only by an information content entity that is about a material component, and that, when filled, prescribes or reports a &apos;has component part&apos; relation between the entities the host and filler information content entities are about</annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition>
		<annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>LA1: if x is a &apos;component parthood slot&apos; then (i) every &apos;has filler&apos; y of x is an &apos;information content entity&apos; that either &apos;is about&apos; some &apos;material component&apos; or &apos;is about&apos; only &apos;material component&apos;, and (ii) x &apos;is slot of&apos; some &apos;information content entity&apos; that either &apos;is about&apos; some &apos;independent continuant&apos; that is not a &apos;spatial region&apos; or &apos;is about&apos; only &apos;independent continuant&apos; that is not &apos;spatial region&apos;</annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
		<annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>LA2: if x is a &apos;component parthood slot&apos; then for any z, y, c, and m, if x is &apos;slot of&apos; z and x &apos;has filler&apos; y, and z &apos;is about&apos; c and y &apos;is about&apos; m, then either c &apos;has component part at some time&apos; m, or z &apos;prescribes&apos; c and if c &apos;conforms to&apos; z then c &apos;has component part at some time &apos; m</annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
		<AnnotationVocabulary:firstOrderLogicAxiom>LA1:ComponentParthoodSlot(x) → ( (∀y(hasFiller(x,y) → (InformationContentEntity(y) ∧ (∃m(MaterialComponent(m) ∧ isAbout(y,m)) ∨ ∀t(isAbout(y,t) → MaterialComponent(t)) )))) ∧ (∃z(isSlotOf(x,z) ∧ InformationContentEntity(z) ∧ (∃c(IndependentContinuant(c) ∧ ¬SpatialRegion(c) ∧ isAbout(z,c)) ∨ ∀u(isAbout(z,u) → (IndependentContinuant(u) ∧ ¬SpatialRegion(u)))))) ) )</AnnotationVocabulary:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
	</owl:Class>
	
	<owl:Class rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/ConnectionSlot">
		<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationSlot"/>
		<rdfs:isDefinedBy>https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/InformationSlot/</rdfs:isDefinedBy>
		<AnnotationVocabulary:firstOrderLogicDefinition>ConnectionSlot(s) ↔ InformationSlot(s) ∧ ∃a&apos;, b&apos; (slotOf(s, a&apos;) ∧ fills(b&apos;, s) ∧ ∀a, b (describes(a&apos;,a) ∧ describes(b&apos;,b) → conencts(a, b)))</AnnotationVocabulary:firstOrderLogicDefinition>
	</owl:Class>
	
	<owl:Class rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/ConnectorSlot">
		<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationSlot"/>
		<rdfs:isDefinedBy>https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/InformationSlot/</rdfs:isDefinedBy>
		<owl:equivalentClass>
			<owl:Class>
				<owl:intersectionOf rdf:parseType="Collection">
					<rdf:Description rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationSlot">
					</rdf:Description>
					<owl:Restriction>
						<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/hasFiller"/>
						<owl:someValuesFrom>
							<owl:Restriction>
								<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/describes"/>
								<owl:someValuesFrom rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/JoiningMaterial"/>
							</owl:Restriction>
						</owl:someValuesFrom>
					</owl:Restriction>
				</owl:intersectionOf>
			</owl:Class>
		</owl:equivalentClass>
		<AnnotationVocabulary:firstOrderLogicDefinition>ConnectionSlot(s) ↔ InformationSlot(s) ∧ ∃a&apos;, b&apos; (slotOf(s, a&apos;) ∧ fills(b&apos;, s) ∧ ∀a, b (describes(a&apos;,a) ∧ describes(b&apos;,b) → hasConnector(a, b)))</AnnotationVocabulary:firstOrderLogicDefinition>
	</owl:Class>
	
	<owl:Class rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/CountExpression">
		<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/ValueExpression"/>
		<rdfs:isDefinedBy>https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/InformationSlot/</rdfs:isDefinedBy>
	</owl:Class>
	
	<owl:Class rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/CountSlot">
		<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationSlot"/>
		<rdfs:isDefinedBy>https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/InformationSlot/</rdfs:isDefinedBy>
		<owl:equivalentClass>
			<owl:Class>
				<owl:intersectionOf rdf:parseType="Collection">
					<rdf:Description rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/InformationSlot">
					</rdf:Description>
					<owl:Restriction>
						<owl:onProperty rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/hasFiller"/>
						<owl:allValuesFrom rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/CountExpression"/>
					</owl:Restriction>
				</owl:intersectionOf>
			</owl:Class>
		</owl:equivalentClass>
	</owl:Class>
	
